      "body" : "Thanks for checking this out. I personally disagree. I think that anyone reading the code knows that there are 86400 seconds in a day, and that 600 seconds is 10 minutes.\r\n\r\nWould you rather see constants for 86400, like DAY, and 10MIN for 600? Or do you prefer 60 * 60 * 24?",
